  <summary date="2023-08-28T21:26:22Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Preventing Illegal Weapons Trafficking Act of 2022

This bill requires federal agencies to develop a strategy to address the trafficking of firearm modification devices that are used to convert weapons into machine guns. It also requires specific reporting on these devices, and it provides for the seizure and forfeiture of proceeds relating to machinegun trafficking.</summary>
